<h1>The Michael J. Fox Foundation and Accordant</h1>
<p class="intro">The Michael J. Fox Foundation’s partnership with Accordant helps us share important Parkinson’s news with more patients — and gives us the chance to hear from you. As you look through research news and resources, we hope you consider getting involved with the Foundation. This year, the answer is in all of us.</p>
<p class="h-divider"> </p>
<h2><a href="/foundation/news.html?tagid=260">Learn more about PD Research</a></h2>
<p>Find events, calls and discussion forums to learn more about our research and engage with the research community.</p>
<p class="h-divider"> </p>
<h2><a href="/get-involved/clinical-trial.html">Find a Clinical Trial</a></h2>
<p>Speeding a PD cure is up to us. Join Fox Trial Finder today to find the clinical trials that need someone like you.</p>
<p class="h-divider"> </p>
<h2><a href="/get-involved/donation.php?fr_id=1600">Donate to Advance Research</a></h2>
<p class="p1">The Michael J. Fox Foundation's single-minded goal is to speed progress in Parkinson's therapeutic development. 88 cents of every dollar we spend goes to our research program efforts and ultimately better treatments for patients. <a href="https://www.michaeljfox.org/get-involved/donation.php?fr_id=2380" class="orange bold">Donate today</a> to advance Parkinson's research.</p>
<p class="h-divider"> </p>
<h2><a href="/get-involved/fundraise.html">Join Team Fox Events</a></h2>
<p>Turn your passions and interests into unique fundraising events and athletics feats. Run a race, host a golf tournament, or throw a pancake breakfast to speed a cure for Parkinson’s. The ideas are endless.</p>
